HEADWORD: Phalanstery
<hw>Phal"an*ster*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>-ies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[F.
<ets>phalanst⟦egrave⟧re</ets>, fr. Gr. <grk>fa`lagx</grk> a phalanx +
